data.description: Welcome to the Gated Community of Pacific Avenue. This beautiful home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, with courtyard. The first floor is an open concept with 9 foot ceilings. The modern opent kitchen includes Stainless Steel appliances, microwave and dishwasher, quartz counter tops and fresh white cabinets, with black hardware. 2 matching high-end black pendent lights located above kitchen island installed for modern luxury. Living room is beautifully equipped with custom, upgraded electric fireplace beneath TV mantel, with upgraded flooring and custom rods and curtains throughout. Upstairs you will find three spacious bedrooms and two complete baths. There are many energy saving features that include a whole house fan, solar, tankless water heater, washer/dryer, and more. Large 2 car garage with custom professional epoxy flooring that can be utilized as a home gym, for entertaining, or to show off your vehicles. The community offers pool, jacuzzi, dog park, club house, and outdoor BBQ's and gathering areas. This home is conveniently located to shopping, schools, medical and the freeway with a low HOA. Enjoy viewing one of the most upgraded, turnkey properties in the whole neighborhood. See it while you can, Enjoy!
